<td valign="MIDDLE"><font face="Verdana" size="2" color="000000">I am on the positive side of this thread.  I have played many classes on this game including all the pure casters and I finally decided that the enchanter is the best (for my playing style)  I am only lvl 6 at the time but I am having the most fun playing this character than I have ever had playing any other class.  Not to mention the Role Playing is great with an enchanter!  I look forward to getting new illusions every time I get new spells.  Do I want to be a human?  A half- elf or high elf?  It's funny to confuse people when I join a group as a human and when some leave to pull something they come back to find a High Elf in the group *giggles*  Isn't playing with minds what we do best?  Anyway, overall I love this class.  I do think that we have a lot to offer ourselves and groups.  It's your own fault if you let others use you solely for Clarity.  You can do a lot more.<p>

Venna<br>
