<td valign="MIDDLE"><font face="Verdana" size="2" color="000000">I played a warrior up to lvl 36 then hit a wall  Couldnt find a group for anything. so i started a enchanter. WOW this is my class.<p>

The key for a enchanter is. DO NOT panic LOL i know it sounds stupid but true. when in a good group or soloing even. never panic  a good enchanter always thinks he is in control or going to get control even until my last sliver of life fades and i die. <p>

 example : cazic thule at lvl 26 in gator alley with a group of 3 people mostly 30 to 34.<br>
me 26th  paladin 34th cleric 33rd.<p>

big pull of 6 gators all red to me  we took them down one at a time  then sat back in amazment at what we had just done with low lost of health. It was amazing. now those 2 people give me a tell everytime i get on a good enchanters name gets around because we make the impossible possible.<p>

The best quote i have heard from anyone is "a good enchanter makes the impossible possible but a bad enchanter will get you killed."<p>

So fellow enchanters get out there read the post study up on your abilities learn em practice em and you will make a name for your self.<p>

sorry just some scattered thoughts.<br>
Kerac <br>
